## Concepts Practiced

### for Loop

Used when the number of iterations is known.

### while Loop

Used when repetition depends on a condition.

### Modulus Operator (%)

Used to extract the last digit.

Example:

123 % 10 = 3

### Floor Division (//)

Used to remove the last digit.

Example:

123 // 10 = 12

